</tr>
<tr>
<td style="font-size: 90%; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; padding: 3px;">Signed<br />
<small>-&#160;location</small></td>
<td align="top" style="font-size: 90%; padding: 3px;">1 July 1968<br />
