<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:NPT_Participation.svg" class="image" title="Participation in the Nuclear Non-Proliferation Treaty     &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Signed and ratified &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Acceded or succeeded &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;State abiding by treaty   &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Withdrawn &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Non-signatory  "><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/NPT_Participation.svg/300px-NPT_Participation.svg.png" width="300" height="132" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
