<li id="cite_note-68"><b><a href="#cite_ref-68" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.state.gov/t/isn/rls/other/81946.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.state.gov/t/isn/rls/other/81946.htm" rel="nofollow">Disarmament, the United States, and the NPT</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-69"><b><a href="#cite_ref-69" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.fco.gov.uk/en/fco-in-action/counter-terrorism/weapons/nuclear-weapons/" class="external text" title="http://www.fco.gov.uk/en/fco-in-action/counter-terrorism/weapons/nuclear-weapons/" rel="nofollow">FCO fact sheet on nuclear weapons</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-70"><b><a href="#cite_ref-70" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.armscontrol.org/act/2005_01-02/Levitte" class="external text" title="http://www.armscontrol.org/act/2005_01-02/Levitte" rel="nofollow">The 2005 NPT Review Conference: A French Perspective</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-71"><b><a href="#cite_ref-71" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.un.org/events/npt2005/statements/npt03russian.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.un.org/events/npt2005/statements/npt03russian.pdf" rel="nofollow">Statement by Russian Deputy Foreign Minister Kislyak at the 2005 NPT Review Conference</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-72"><b><a href="#cite_ref-72" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.un.org/NPT2010/SecondSession/delegates%20statements/P5%20Statement.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.un.org/NPT2010/SecondSession/delegates%20statements/P5%20Statement.pdf" rel="nofollow">Statement of the P5 to the 2008 NPT PrepCom</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
